{"tid":469102,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個扑野被撞破經歷","createTime":"2017-11-15T03:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T09:37:12.000Z","uid":153790,"like":2,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a67265f76360bab0fea8ace277804d0254728b6e","tid":469102,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"我有2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次係自己屋企同女朋友水深火熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n準備破處 唔洗帶套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老豆番左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢無即刻入屋 係門口執野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢未知我女友黎左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即刻鳩縮 同女友9秒9著衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我女友即刻醒水 叫我著完出去叫老豆先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢著好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n仲有一次 今次係佢老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係女友張床到互摸到水深火熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我準備破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌 到佢老豆番黎 佢老豆好快咁開大門入左屋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街了 衫都著唔切 <br />\n我女友衣衫襤褸咁出左去應付佢老豆<br />\n我叫左聲叔叔就走撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌<br />\n<br />\n最後旅行破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de37e97552b0965c10654c0fe1412e09f2287047","tid":469102,"uid":142481,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"我都想可以俾人撞破<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"